What great discourse, from Tao Guo who tells us what he thinks from his Asian perspective, which alot of you seem to want to fight him over rather than listen to him, I mean you didn't walk behind his water buffalo or in his sandles, right?, to Cook B. (aka John Wayne) and his &quot;never say die&quot; mentality, who continues to see domino's and sampan's landing in Santa Monica, and Arthur, who must read this place daily, if not hourly, and now a riff between John R. and Tom Dier, and frankly, I think Tom hits the politically correct or incorrect nail RIGHT on the head, we are a site still alive. And we are all honest men with honest convictions to state, except one. There is one dog lurking and waiting to lick up the scraps.<br><br>
Of course, when the veterans, the victims, the protestors, and the real participants are sharing, comes Nurse Ratchet. Ol Nurse, who is a high school teacher who silently did nothing during the war while millions died, coward with no name nor e mail address, and now calls himself &quot;doc's mistress&quot;. Just what I needed. I guess gender confusion fits him as well.  Hey Nurse, bend over somewhere else. Don't try and ruin the flow here between serious discussion with your air head textbook marxist babble. <br><br>
The interaction between Tom Dier, Tao Guo, and John Ratcliff, have been the essensce of the war, of evil and communism, of good and country. I guess it is too much for Nurse Ratchet, so he tries to deflect the conversation away from the meat, to the fat, where he lives and thinks. He can't handle the real issues, so he snipes again at the players he so envys. God Damn, but he grows weary. I must learn to ignore him as the rest of you do, but I get weak at times. (Arthur, please, no comments).<br><br>
Once again, when Nurse Ratchet's antique thinking is exposed, he trys and belittles others.  The pattern is stale, and by now, ignored by most of you.  My nemesis nurse, you are one sick puppy, still trying to convince others, outside of your classroom, that communism is good, and the USofA is bad.  <br><br>
In case no one has noticed, which I doubt, all you (dear nurse) to is put down the American fighting soldier. Insult upon insult riddles your post.  That is exactly why everyone else but me ignores you.  I couldn't resist, being that you now think you are my mistress.  What a stupid punk you are.<br>
Go back to your textbooks, or to your dogma, but for god sakes, let the real story tellers, the Toms', Arts, Andys, the guys in the bush, tell their tales. Slinky dog that you are, have no tail at all to tell, so crawl back to your students, (unless that too is a lie) and put on your vest of false bravado, and continue to live your miserable life on nothingness, but &quot;my mistress&quot;, sorry pal, not a chance. I'd amputate sooner.   Yes, Art, I have flamed again.<br><br>
